texts.text: TU27 was a version of Xbox 360 Edition released on July 24, 2015.[1] This version is based on Java Edition 1.6.1. This version was reuploaded. [edit]

Added Greek Mythology Mash-up pack trial content
Acacia and dark oak wood, planks, fences, fence gates, doors, slabs and stairs have been added to the Creative inventory.

MCCE-68 – The crafting recipe for dispensers accepts damaged bows.
MCCE-69 – The crafting recipe for carrot on a stick accepts damaged fishing rods.
MCCE-154 – Players without privileges can make your pet stand up.
MCCE-318 – Leads stay on fences when the animal is killed.
MCCE-351 – Location-based crashes.
MCCE-421 – Oak door recipe only gives 1 door instead of 3.
MCCE-447 – Bug when closing game on PS4 after loading a game about 5 minutes after loading a world.
MCCE-452 – Playing on creative world makes the game randomly close on PlayStation 3 and 4.
MCCE-497 – Lead role issue with new fences.
Fixed an issue with wolves not taking damage properly.
